ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectAppointment of the Honorable Karina Gould and the Honourable Steven MacKinnon
PrecisOrder (1) terminating the appointments made by Order in Council P.C.2021-992 of December 1, 2021; and (2) appointing the Honourable KARINA GOULD and the Honourable STEVEN MACKINONN , members of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, to be members of the Board of Internal Economy of the House of Commons.
